        <h3>About the Hotel</h3>
        <p>Basma Aswan Hotel Located on the highest hills in Aswan, Basma Hotel Aswan offers unique views of the Nile.<br>The hotel serves daily breakfast buffets. Guests can enjoy fresh fruit juices on Basma's rooftop terrace, while enjoying stunning views of the Nile Valley. The restaurant offers a wide choice of meals.

The hotel is a 15-minute drive from the Aswan High Dam, and the road next to the Nile in central Aswan is 2 km from the hotel.

